room_title: Escape room "Uncle Ernie's Millions" by Escape the Room Challenge in Cincinnati
room_description: There's a fortune to be had, and the real will must be hidden somewhere in your late uncle's cabinet. However, dictated by his official last will and testament, the money goes to a charity run by his shady lawyer. That can't be a coincidence! Determined to find out the truth, you sneak into your uncle's game room. You have an hour before the reading of the will - hurry!
